title: DORAEMON NOBITA NO BOKUJOU MONOGATARI TO INCLUDE CHINESE SUPPORT
body: Bandai Namco has announced that the upcoming Doraemon Nobita no Bokujou Monogatari is going to include both Simplified and Traditional Chinese. The title will launch in Hong Kong and Taiwan, and it’s coming out at the same time as the Japanese release..

summary: BEST BUY OFFERING FREE STEELBOOK WITH PURCHASE OF POKEMON: LET'S GO STARTING FEB. 17TH, 2019
title: BEST BUY OFFERING FREE STEELBOOK WITH PURCHASE OF POKEMON: LET'S GO STARTING FEB. 17TH, 2019
body:
Who doesn’t like a good steelbook? If you like the one you see above, you might want to make your way to a Best Buy starting Feb. 17th, 2019. The retailer has announced that they’ll be throwing in the above steelbook for free with a purchase of Pokemon: Let’s GO.

For those who’ve already purchased the game, it might not hurt to take your Best Buy receipt in to argue your case. You might be able to convince them to let you walk away with the case. Best of luck to anyone who tries

tags: toejam & earl: back in the groove
summary: TOEJAM & EARL: BACK IN THE GROOVE'S REGULAR AND LIMITED EDITIONS AVAILABLE TO PREORDER
title: TOEJAM & EARL: BACK IN THE GROOVE'S REGULAR AND LIMITED EDITIONS AVAILABLE TO PREORDER
body:
ToeJam & Earl: Back in the Groove on physical cartridge for the Nintendo Switch. Region free. The Collector’s Edition is limited to just 2,500 copies!

Includes groovin’ reversible art and a full-color manual.

The Collector’s Edition includes:

4 enamel pins featuring the game’s main characters
2 enamel pin blind boxes, each featuring one unique Earthling pin
A 25-piece puzzle recreating a map from the game
10 pin stands to set your pins up on the map
Various environment standees to embellish your map
18 x 24 inch poster
The game soundtrack on physical cassette tape

Grab your preorders here

summary: Nintendo Consoles Timeline 🎮 I made a Nintendo timeline for all of the Nintendo consoles and their sales. The Nintendo Switch...
caption:
Nintendo Consoles Timeline 🎮

I made a Nintendo timeline for all of the Nintendo consoles and their sales.

The Nintendo Switch has already beaten the Gamecube in sales and has probably already beaten the Nintendo 64 since it’s sales were released last year, which will make it Nintendo’s best selling 3D home console of all time! Quite impressive for a console that’s less than two years old!


- This post will be updated when new sales figures are released

- My consoles pattern collection

title: Final Fantasy IX para Switch es la misma versión que PC y móvil, con todo y errores
